'''2011年[[全英音樂獎|全英音樂獎]]'''在2011年2月15日舉行。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nme.com/news/arcade-fire/54559|title=Arcade Fire, Mumford & Sons, The xx up for Brit Awards|date=2011-01-13|work=NME|accessdate=2011-01-14|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304113942/http://www.nme.com/news/arcade-fire/54559|dead-url=no}}</ref>本屆為第31屆[[英國唱片業協會|英國唱片業協會]]年度流行音樂獎項。本屆也是首次離開[[伯爵宮展覽中心|Earls Court]]，前往同樣位在倫敦的 [[O2體育館|The O2 Arena]] 舉行。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2011/jan/13/brit-awards-tinie-tempah-nominations|title=Brit awards: Tinie Tempah shines with four nominations|date=2011-01-13|work=Guardian|accessdate=2011-01-14|archive-date=2011-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111220040650/http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2011/jan/13/brit-awards-tinie-tempah-nominations|dead-url=no}}</ref> 主持人為[[詹姆士·柯登|詹姆士·柯登]]（James Corden）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12182834|title=Tinie Tempah nominated for four Brit Awards|date=2011-01-13|work=BBC News|accessdate=2011-01-14|archive-date=2011-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110114050304/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12182834|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/artists/tinie-tempah/news/253396-tinie-tempah-brit-awards-jessie-j-plan-b|title=Tinie Tempah Reacts To BRIT Award Nominations|date=2011-01-14|work=MTV.co.uk|accessdate=2011-01-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110117113514/http://www.mtv.co.uk/artists/tinie-tempah/news/253396-tinie-tempah-brit-awards-jessie-j-plan-b|archivedate=2011-01-17}}</ref> [[天霸泰尼|天霸泰尼]]與[[拱廊之火|拱廊之火]]各贏得兩座獎項。<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.nme.com/news/tinie-tempah/54990|title=Tinie Tempah wins British Single gong at Brit Awards 2011|date=2011-02-15|work=NME.com|accessdate=2011-02-15|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304104936/http://www.nme.com/news/tinie-tempah/54990|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2011/feb/15/brit-awards-2011-take-that|title=Brit awards 2011: Take That win best British group 21 years after their debut|date=2011-02-15|work=Guardian|accessdate=2011-02-15|archive-date=2021-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303093941/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2011/feb/15/brit-awards-2011-take-that}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12463741|title=Best group Brit goes to Take That|date=2011-02-15|work=BBC News|accessdate=2011-02-15|archive-date=2011-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110216045818/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12463741|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2011年被譽為是全英音樂獎的重新出發－移師新場地、知名設計師[[薇薇安·魏斯伍德|薇薇安·魏斯伍德]]設計新獎座、更強調在音樂上，特別是現場演出。雖然這些改變普遍受到歡迎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12472422|title=Brit awards: Verdict on the 'new' show|work=BBC News|accessdate=2011-02-16|archive-date=2011-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110216050916/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12472422|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但觀眾數卻是五年來新低<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12463741|title=Brit awards hit by ratings slump|work=BBC News|accessdate=2011-02-16|archive-date=2011-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110216045818/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12463741|dead-url=no}}</ref>，平均480萬人，最高590萬人。相對的，第四頻道的《Big Fat Gypsy Weddings》完結篇吸引了650觀眾收看。

